      Added privilege types for the user. The user can only be assigned three possible chars for their privilege. If a user has a u, they are a general user and have all normal functionalities in the app. If the user has the char g, they are a group leader and can manage the group that they own. Finally, if the user has a char b, then they are banned and will not be able to do anything within the app. The full functionality may be implemented in other issues.
